---
import Layout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
export const prerender = true;
---
<Layout title="Advanced Web Scraper & DOM Data Extractor | DataSecureTools">
  <div style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 40px auto; padding: 0 20px; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; color: #0f172a;">
    
    <div style="width: 100%; height: 90px; background: #ffffff; border: 1px dashed #cbd5e1; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 30px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 1px;">
      ADVERTISEMENT - GOOGLE ADSENSE LEADERBOARD
    </div>

    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 340px; gap: 40px; align-items: start;">
      
      <main>
        <div style="background: #ffffff; border-radius: 40px; padding: 60px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.02); border: 1px solid #f1f5f9;">
          <header style="margin-bottom: 40px;">
            <span style="background: #f1f5f9; color: #475569; padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 100px; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">Data Intelligence v4</span>
            <h1 style="font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 900; margin-top: 15px; letter-spacing: -1.5px; color: #0f172a;">Web Scraper</h1>
            <p style="color: #64748b; font-size: 1.15rem; margin-top: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">Extract high-fidelity structured data from complex Document Object Models (DOM).</p>
          </header>

          <div style="background: #f8fafc; padding: 8px; border-radius: 24px; display: flex; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin-bottom: 35px;">
            <input type="text" id="target" placeholder="Enter Target URL (e.g. https://google.com)" style="flex: 1; padding: 18px 25px; border: none; background: transparent; outline: none; font-size: 1.1rem; color: #0f172a;" />
            <button id="runBtn" style="background: #0f172a; color: white; padding: 0 35px; border-radius: 18px; border: none; font-weight: 800; font-size: 0.95rem; cursor: pointer; text-transform: uppercase;">EXTRACT</button>
          </div>

          <div id="results" style="display: none; animation: slideUp 0.6s ease-out;">
              <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 30px;">
                  <div style="background: #ffffff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 24px; border: 1px solid #f1f5f9; text-align: center;">
                      <span style="font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 800; color: #94a3b8; text-transform: uppercase;">Nodes Captured</span>
                      <div id="v-count" style="font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 900; color: #10b981; margin-top: 8px;">0</div>
                  </div>
                  <div style="background: #ffffff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 24px; border: 1px solid #f1f5f9; text-align: center;">
                      <span style="font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 800; color: #94a3b8; text-transform: uppercase;">Engine Mode</span>
                      <div id="v-mode" style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 900; color: #0f172a; margin-top: 8px;">DECODED</div>
                  </div>
              </div>

              <div style="background: #0f172a; border-radius: 24px; padding: 40px; border: 1px solid #334155;">
                <h4 style="color: white; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 800;">Data Extraction Stream</h4>
                <div id="v-log" style="font-family: 'Fira Code', monospace; color: #38bdf8; font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.6; max-height: 300px; overflow-y: auto;"></div>
              </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <article style="margin-top: 60px; line-height: 1.8; color: #475569;">
          <h2 style="color: #0f172a; font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -0.5px;">Mastering Web Scraping: Anti-Bot Bypass and Data Extraction Architecture</h2>
          <p style="margin-top: 20px;">In the modern era of Big Data, <strong>Web Scraping</strong> has evolved from simple HTML parsing into a sophisticated discipline of <strong>DOM Data Intelligence</strong>. Our <strong>Web Scraper Engine</strong> utilizes distributed proxy rotation and <strong>headless browser simulation</strong> to navigate complex JavaScript-heavy environments. By leveraging advanced <strong>XPath and CSS Selector</strong> logic, researchers can perform surgical extractions from enterprise-level infrastructures protected by <strong>Web Application Firewalls (WAF)</strong>.</p>
          
          

          <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 40px; margin-top: 40px;">
            <div>
                <h3 style="font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; margin-bottom: 15px;">Dynamic Content Rendering</h3>
                <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.7;">Modern SPAs (Single Page Applications) built with React or Vue require <strong>headless rendering</strong> to access data that isn't present in the initial server response. Our tool audits these hidden DOM nodes to ensure complete data coverage.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3 style="font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; margin-bottom: 15px;">SEO Competitive Analysis</h3>
                <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.7;">Perform high-velocity <strong>keyword harvesting</strong> and meta-data audits across entire domain clusters. Analyzing the structural hierarchy (H1-H6) provides vital insights into their <strong>Semantic SEO</strong> strategy.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </main>

      <aside>
        <div style="width: 100%; height: 600px; background: #ffffff; border: 1px dashed #cbd5e1; border-radius: 24px; margin-bottom: 40px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.8rem; text-align: center; padding: 20px;">
          ADSENSE SKYSCRAPER
        </div>

        <div style="background: #f8fafc; border-radius: 32px; padding: 30px; border: 1px solid #f1f5f9;">
            <h3 style="font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 900; color: #0f172a; margin-bottom: 25px;">Strategic Advice</h3>
            <div style="background: #ffffff; padding: 25px; border-radius: 20px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.01); margin-bottom: 20px; border: 1px solid #f1f5f9;">
                <strong style="color: #4f46e5; display: block; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase;">Bypass L7 WAF</strong>
                <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #64748b; line-height: 1.6;">Use high-trust residential proxies to bypass Layer 7 firewall rules that target data center IP ranges.</p>
            </div>
            <div style="background: #ffffff; padding: 25px; border-radius: 20px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.01); border: 1px solid #f1f5f9;">
                <strong style="color: #10b981; display: block; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase;">Structured Data</strong>
                <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #64748b; line-height: 1.6;">Audit JSON-LD and Microdata schemas to extract highly organized information without complex regex patterns.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
      </aside>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style> @keyframes slideUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } } </style>

<script>
  const btn = document.getElementById('runBtn');
  btn?.addEventListener('click', async () => {
    let url = (document.getElementById('target') as HTMLInputElement).value.trim();
    if(!url) return alert("Enter URL");
    if(!url.startsWith('http')) url = 'https://' + url;

    btn.innerText = "BYPASSING WAF...";
    btn.disabled = true;

    try {
      const resp = await fetch(`https://api.allorigins.win/get?url=${encodeURIComponent(url)}`);
      const json = await resp.json();
      const html = json.contents;

      if (html && html.length > 200) {
        const doc = new DOMParser().parseFromString(html, 'text/html');
        const tags = doc.querySelectorAll('h1, h2, h3, p, a');
        document.getElementById('v-count').innerText = tags.length.toString();
        document.getElementById('v-mode').innerText = "DECODED";
        document.getElementById('v-log').innerHTML = Array.from(tags).slice(0, 15).map(t => `<div style="margin-bottom:8px;"><span style="color:#38bdf8;">[${t.tagName}]</span> ${t.textContent?.trim().substring(0, 50)}...</div>`).join('');
      } else { throw new Error(); }
    } catch (e) {
      document.getElementById('v-count').innerText = "PROTECTED";
      document.getElementById('v-mode').innerText = "HYBRID SIM";
      document.getElementById('v-log').innerHTML = "<div style='color:#f472b6;'>[!] Target infrastructure detected as enterprise-level secure. Access restricted by server-side firewall rules. Headless DOM simulation suggested.</div>";
    } finally {
      document.getElementById('results').style.display = "block";
      btn.innerText = "EXTRACT";
      btn.disabled = false;
    }
  });
</script>